description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Cherry blossoms and canola flowers
-Rice field scenery in autumn
-Mt.Fuji is reflected in the water
-Winter seaside
-Valley with autumn leaves
-Red bridge and autumn leaves
-River surrounded by fresh greenery
-Paddy field under the summer sky
-A blue train running along the coastline
-Red bridge reflected on the mountainside
name: Japan's Most Scenic Train Trips
